properties.sfomuseum:description: Handwritten letter from Harold M. Bixby to his wife, Debby Bixby, dated June 23, [1933], on stationery from China Airways Federal Inc.; typewritten header; includes information about purchased mandarin-style coats and material; [Paul] Groeger’s return to Shanghai; mentions Miss Forbes.
